# Development Workflow

## Tools and Configuration
- Node.js version is specified in [.nvmrc](mdc:.nvmrc)
- Package management with pnpm ([pnpm-lock.yaml](mdc:pnpm-lock.yaml))
- ESLint configuration in [eslint.config.js](mdc:eslint.config.js)
- Prettier configuration in [.prettierrc.json](mdc:.prettierrc.json)
- Git hooks managed by Husky in `.husky/` directory
- VS Code settings in `.vscode/` directory

## Quality Standards
1. All TypeScript files must follow the configuration in [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)
2. Code formatting is enforced by Prettier
3. Code quality is enforced by ESLint
4. Git commits should follow conventional commit format

## CI/CD
- GitLab CI configuration in [.gitlab-ci.yml](mdc:.gitlab-ci.yml)
- Build artifacts are generated in the `dist/` directory
